rows.label: qst200913_msg002
rows.name:
Oh no! He's being attacked
by the Tirkin tribe! We
have to help him quickly!

rows.label: qst200913_msg003
rows.name:
Go away, mo! Kupon is
not your food, mo!

rows.label: qst200913_msg005
rows.name:
Kasane?! This is bad, mo!
Don't you come here, mo!

rows.label: qst200913_msg006
rows.name: It's alright now! I'll save you!

rows.label: qst200913_msg007
rows.name: No, mo! Don't come any closer, mo!!

rows.label: qst200913_msg010
rows.name: ...It seems we have to help him again.
